# AGENTS.md - Aqiu's Blog

## Project Overview

This is a **personal technical blog** hosted on GitHub Pages, generated using the [Hexo](https://hexo.io/) static site generator (version 8.0.0). The blog supports both Chinese (zh-CN) and English (en) content and focuses on programming, databases, and distributed systems.

- **Website**: https://aqiu16717.github.io/
- **Repository**: https://github.com/Aqiu16717/Aqiu16717.github.io
- **Author**: aq1u
- **Email**: aqiu16717@gmail.com
- **Generator**: Hexo 8.0.0
- **Theme**: Cactus Dark (a clean, minimal, responsive theme)

### Repository Branches

This repository has two main branches:

| Branch | Purpose | Content |
|--------|---------|---------|
| `source` | Development | Hexo source files (Markdown posts, configs, themes) |
| `main` | Production | Generated static HTML files (GitHub Pages serves this) |

**Current branch**: `main` (contains the compiled static site)

## Technology Stack

### Core Technologies
- **Hexo 8.0.0** - Fast, simple & powerful blog framework
- **Node.js** - Runtime for Hexo (required for development)
- **EJS** - Templating engine
- **Stylus** - CSS preprocessor
- **Markdown** - Content format

### npm Scripts (from source branch)
```json
{
  "build": "hexo generate",
  "clean": "hexo clean",
  "deploy": "hexo deploy",
  "server": "hexo server"
}
```

### Frontend Libraries
| Library | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| jQuery 3.x | DOM manipulation and event handling |
| Font Awesome 6.x | Icon library |
| Clipboard.js | Code block copy functionality |
| Justified Gallery | Image gallery layout |

### Hexo Plugins
- `hexo-deployer-git` - Git deployment
- `hexo-generator-archive` - Archive pages generator
- `hexo-generator-category` - Category pages generator
- `hexo-generator-feed` - RSS/Atom feed generator
- `hexo-generator-index` - Index page generator
- `hexo-generator-tag` - Tag pages generator
- `hexo-renderer-ejs` - EJS renderer
- `hexo-renderer-marked` - Markdown renderer
- `hexo-renderer-stylus` - Stylus renderer
- `hexo-server` - Local development server

### Comments & Analytics
- **Giscus** - GitHub Discussions-based comment system
  - Repository: `Aqiu16717/Aqiu16717.github.io`
  - Category: `Announcements`
- Reserved placeholders for: Google Analytics, Umami, Baidu Analytics, Cloudflare Analytics

